cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language generation and knowledge graphs, which are both topics that fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which is a common theme in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of knowledge graphs.
